    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I fail to see why is that restrictive. Those are duplicated cameos stored within the sidebar mixes.\n\nNow why remapping them won't work: they do not share the color index. What you propose is to have a PlayerColorPalette trait variant which can remap different colors based upon race. Also I'm not even certain if remapping those can be done without AA issues, considering that the TS cameo palette is a funky rainbow.\n\nFor the record, the GDI refinery uses colors around 90 for the gold, but the Nod refinery cameo uses colors around 18 - yet they share the base palette.\n\n![icons](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1136302/8895291/eae7e454-33d4-11e5-90a1-e9a727c02091.png)\n"
  },
